UC16 ..> UC20 : <<include>>
UC17 ..> UC20 : <<include>>
UC18 ..> UC20 : <<include>>

' BACnet → YABE
UC20 --> YABE : BACnet/IP UDP 47808\nWrite AO/BO/MV

' SQLite
